channel.description:
I found this amazing server on the net, off the top of my head it has:
Fightable NPCs Accurate combat + total level formula Talking bankers Trading [yesss!] Accurate armor and weapon bonuses!!! Accurate display of current weapon in the change attack style box & much more
Scanned and clean! Now Remember, this is NOT MADE MY ME, all credit goes to Masterhoulahan Ok, I've had my fun,now you have yours!
Download Link: http://www.filefactory.com/get/f.php?f=40dcdf7c26ec3666aac87d1f
